                <div class="key-insight">
                    <strong>Critical Issue:</strong> Core team (GM + Oscar + Mikey) alone costs $11,994/month = 19% of sales. At industry standard 30% total labor, only $6,936/month remains for all other staff, security, and operations.
                </div>
