            <div class="section">
                <div class="section-title">Food Cost Context: Early Stage Operations</div>
                
                <div class="methodology-box">
                    <strong>November Food Cost:</strong> 33.2% of sales ($20,977.30). This is higher than mature industry standard (28-30%) but expected for a restaurant in its first full month of operations without economies of scale. As sales volume increases, food cost percentage should naturally decrease through better purchasing power, reduced waste, and operational efficiency.
                </div>
                
