                </table>
                
                <div class="methodology-box">
                    <strong>Conclusion:</strong> Current staffing level is appropriate for a restaurant generating $174,383/month at industry standard labor ratios, or $130,788/month at 40% labor. At actual sales of $63,099/month, the restaurant is staffed at 2.76x the appropriate level.
                </div>
