                    â€¢ <strong>Scenario 2 (13 staff):</strong> Right-sized for current sales - sustainable operations<br>
                    â€¢ <span style="background: #C6EFCE; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 3px; color: #006100; font-weight: bold;">KEEP</span> = Essential, do not cut<br>
                    â€¢ <span style="background: #FFEB9C; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 3px; color: #9C5700; font-weight: bold;">MAYBE</span> = Evaluate based on schedule needs<br>
                    â€¢ <span style="background: #FFC7CE; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 3px; color: #9C0006; font-weight: bold;">CUT</span> = Not essential to scenario
                </div>
                
