        <!-- SCENARIO 1: SURVIVAL MODE -->
        <div id="scenario1" class="tab-content">
            <div class="alert alert-warning">
                <div class="alert-icon">âš ï¸</div>
                <div>
                    <strong>Scenario 1: Survival Mode - 43% Labor</strong><br>
                    This represents the absolute minimum to keep the business operational while cutting labor nearly in half. Still unprofitable, but stops catastrophic bleeding. Requires keeping core team plus skeleton crew.
                </div>
