                    <ul style="margin: 0.5rem 0 0 1.5rem;">
                        <li>Standard hours (no late-night premium)</li>
                        <li>Higher sales volume for efficiency</li>
                        <li>No security requirements</li>
                        <li>Minimal management overhead</li>
                    </ul>
                    <br>
                    Fast Times operates until 4am on weekends with mandatory security, generating 25%+ of revenue during expensive late-night hours. A 48% labor ratio represents proper staffing for this unique operating model at current volume.
